    "patch_code": "private static long greatestCommonDivisor(long u, long v) {\n    if(u == 0){\n        return Math.abs((int)v);\n    }else if(v == 0){\n        return Math.abs((int)u);\n    }\n    int shift = 0;\n    while(((u & 1) == 0) && ((v & 1) == 0)){\n        u >>= 1;\n        v >>= 1;\n        shift++;\n    }\n    while((u & 1) == 0){\n        u >>= 1;\n    }\n    while(v != 0){\n        while((v & 1) == 0){\n            v >>= 1;\n        }\n        if(u > v){\n            long temp = v;\n            v = u;\n            u = temp;\n        }\n        v = v - u;\n    }\n    return u << shift;\n}",
