    "patch_code": "private static int greatestCommonDivisor(int a, int b) {\n    int old_a, old_b;\n    old_a = a < 0 ? -a : a;\n    old_b = b < 0 ? -b : b;\n    boolean sign = false;\n    if((a ^ b) < 0){\n        sign = true;\n    }\n    while(a != 0){\n       int temp = a;\n       a = b % a;\n       b = temp;\n    }\n    int gcd = old_a * old_b / (sign ? -b : b);\n    return gcd;\n}",
